name: electricity, medium voltage, municipal waste incineration, import from Germany | electricity, medium voltage | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/24951/documentation

This dataset represents the amount of imported electricity generated from wastes, from DE to CH. The import volume is defined directly in the Swiss market mix, this is in the dataset market for electricity, medium voltage, CH. It is therefore set to rero in this dataset.;For a discussion of different ways of modeling electricity trade in LCI, please refer to (Itten & Frischknecht 2012).

This activity represents the point of "handing over" the electricity from one country to the other at the border.

This dataset doesn't include any electricity losses or transmission infrastructure as these are accounted for in the market datasets.
